%section.features.no-padding-bottom
	.container
		.row.double-margin-bottom
			.col.text-center
				%h3.bold-font
					Making healthcare work better
				%p.body-large
					More patient work. Less paperwork. Here’s what Wallet can do for you.
%section.swiper-section
	.swiper-wrapper
		.container
			.row
				.col
					.swiper-container
						.swiper-wrapper
							.swiper-slide 
								.slide-inner.no-padding-top.no-padding-bottom
									.row.align-items-center
										.col-md-6.order-md-2
											%img.img-fluid.mx-auto.d-block{:src=>"../images/slide-1.svg"}
										.col-md-6.order-md-1
											.swiper-content-wrapper
												%p.bold-font.body-large
													Everthing consolidated.
												%p
													Rather than submitting multiple applications, simply maintain one portfolio in EverCheck Wallet. Then, share it with hospitals and facilities digitally.
							.swiper-slide 
								.slide-inner.no-padding-top.no-padding-bottom
									.row.align-items-center
										.col-md-6.order-md-2
											%img.img-fluid.mx-auto.d-block{:src=>"../images/slide-2.svg"}
										.col-md-6.order-md-1
											.swiper-content-wrapper
												%p.bold-font.body-large
													Stay on top of expirables automatically.
												%p
													Wallet alerts you when you have a license or other expirable coming due for renewal. It’s like a personal assistant for your healthcare credentials. 
							.swiper-slide 
								.slide-inner.no-padding-top.no-padding-bottom
									.row.align-items-center
										.col-md-6.order-md-2
											%img.img-fluid.mx-auto.d-block{:src=>"../images/slide-3.svg"}
										.col-md-6.order-md-1
											.swiper-content-wrapper
												%p.bold-font.body-large
													Manage your workplaces in one app.
												%p
													See what your employers have on record for you, and share any updates with them all at once rather than individually.


						.swiper-pagination

						.swiper-button-prev
						.swiper-button-next




%section.verifications
