		.row.double-margin-bottom
			.col.text-center
				%h3.bold-font
					150+ million verifications performed each year
				%p.body-large
					Backed by the power of the nation’s leading credentials verification organization, EverCheck Wallet sends your verified credentials to healthcare organizations securely. 
		.row
			.col-md-4
				.padded
					%img.mx-auto.d-block.margin-bottom{:src=>"../images/verification-lock.svg"}
					%p.body-large.text-center.medium-font
						Your information is 
						%br
						yours. 
					%p.extra-light-text-color
						We never share it with anyone without your permission, and we only share what’s needed for your continued employment.
			.col-md-4
				.padded
					%img.mx-auto.d-block.margin-bottom{:src=>"../images/verification-shield.svg"}
					%p.body-large.text-center.medium-font
						Security is our 
						%br
						priority.  
					%p.extra-light-text-color
						EverCheck Wallet uses industry-standard encryption methods to keep your information secure.
			.col-md-4
				.padded
					%img.mx-auto.d-block.margin-bottom{:src=>"../images/verification-support.svg"}
					%p.body-large.text-center.medium-font
